      "writtenOn": "2020-03-10T17:28:38Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "WDYT if we pass all invocations to be included in one string and all invocations to be removed in another string to make the command line more explicit?\n\nsomething like:\n\nrdb update-inclusions -include \"inv1 inv2 ...\" -remove \"inv3 inv4 ...\"",
