        "id": 1157909
      },
      "writtenOn": "2020-03-10T18:12:17Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I think for rdb-ls it should be fine since we are performing the same action on all the invocation ids.\n\nBut here we can either include or remove invocation ids, so I think it would be nice to be more explicit.",
